; Regression test for issue #1656: Payee tag on first posting affects entire transaction
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1656
; When a Payee tag is applied to a specific posting, only that posting should
; display the tag's payee; other postings should still show the transaction payee.

2018-06-01 Foo
    Liabilities:Credit Card                            -100.00 USD
    ; Payee: Bar
    Expenses:Food                                        50.00 USD
    Expenses:Drink                                       50.00 USD

test reg
18-Jun-01 Bar                   Liabilitie:Credit Card  -100.00 USD  -100.00 USD
          Foo                   Expenses:Food             50.00 USD   -50.00 USD
                                Expenses:Drink            50.00 USD            0
end test
